{"tid":1601110,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"各位同學參與罷課時千其唔好影響到學業","createTime":"2019-09-29T02:02:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T11:56:18.000Z","uid":296693,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"adc819f7b25fa1c03befb13b0872b3335f83bfaa","tid":1601110,"uid":296693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T02:02:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://www.brightstars-hk.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brightstars-hk.com&d=kT0D7NwRktyFNYuHQ%2Fv%2Be%2FUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=d0a98fc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.brightstars-hk.com</a><br />\n<br />\n學霸嘅入嚟義教，唔識嘅入嚟問問題，入邊仲有大量 past paper, question bank, notes, 中學 mock etc<br />\n<br />\n比 WhatsApp / telegram / forum 好嘅原因:<br />\n1. 集合全港手足，冇群組人數限制<br />\n2. 每一個答案，全世界都可以見到<br />\n3. 問完問題可以答，答完問題可以問，無分你我，識答嘅就幫<br />\n4. 集合海量文件，網站註冊係英國，唔會俾人 take down <br />\n5. 下載 Wix App 就可以令手機收到通知<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">麻煩各位義教去幫手答問題<br />\n麻煩各位教師 upload 教學資源<br />\n麻煩各位學生盡情問問題同埋比 developer 意見<br />\n</span><br />\nCustom app 正在研發中，將來會將成個平台般去 iOS / Android app<br />\n<br />\n#930大罷課</span>"},{"pid":"2d03fa8ba86603731bd663a139a366c2f29a938b","tid":1601110,"uid":168161,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T02:05:38.000Z","msg":"好想俾姐姐捉住隻手仔 瘋狂學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(利申 中學雞 全部純whatsapp文字補習?)"},{"pid":"e03ffc70bb4804caeae66152c4a5c59d02d50137","tid":1601110,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T02:06:09.000Z","msg":"義補咪得  網上教得幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fbee927e89cf811491dd12f20a5f1dcd48c8200","tid":1601110,"uid":69484,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:01:11.